# content
contentTitle: Jack Howard
contentTitleAbbreviation: JH
contentSubtitle: Principal Software Engineer at Expel
firstLinkURL: https://github.com/JackHowa
firstLinkTitle: GitHub
secondLinkURL: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JPtng2eFAZc
